 of the <i>-n-</i> (compare   Menzies  ).","History: This is the name of a Scottish Highland clan, historically associated with the mountainous district of Kintail in nortwestern Scotland, with Cromarty, and with Loch Seaforth (Loch Shiphoirt) on the Island of Harris."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Mary-nic-Alexander Mackenzie of Applecross and Coul was born as the daughter of Alexander Mackenzie of Kintail - progenitor of Coul and Applecross and Christine Munro of Assynt, latterly Applecross and Coul. She had at least 2 sons and 5 daughters with John-mac-Alexander Chisholme of Comar - 16th of Chisholme."},"et":{"–":"Surnud","1617–1681":"1617–1681","–1639":"–1639","–Male":"Surnud","–Female":"Surnud","1615–1677":"1615–1677","–1622":"–1622","–1627":"–1627","–1659":"–1659","1570–1650":"1570–1650","1574–1647":"1574–1647","from about 1615 to 1617":"umbes 1615 kuni 1617","1681":"1681","1570":"1570","1622":"1622","1677":"1677","1574":"1574","1650":"1650","1639":"1639","1617":"1617","1627":"1627","1659":"1659","1615":"1615","1647":"1647"},"fi":{"–":"Kuollut","1617–1681":"1617–1681","–1639":"–1639","–Male":"Kuollut","–Female":"Kuollut","1615–1677":"1615–1677","–1622":"–1622","–1627":"–1627","–1659":"–1659","1570–1650":"1570–1650","1574–1647":"1574–1647","from about 1615 to 1617":"vuodesta noin 1615 vuoteen 1617","1681":"1681","1570":"1570","1622":"1622","1677":"1677","1574":"1574","1650":"1650","1639":"1639","1617":"1617","1627":"1627","1659":"1659","1615":"1615","1647":"1647"},"fr":{"–":"Décédée","1617–1681":"1617–1681","–1639":"–1639","–Male":"Décédé","–Female":"Décédée","1615–1677":"1615–1677","–1622":"–1622","–1627":"–1627","–1659":"–1659","1570–1650":"1570–1650","1574–1647":"1574–1647","from about 1615 to 1617":"du environ 1615 au 1617","1681":"1681","1570":"1570","1622":"1622","1677":"1677","1574":"1574","1650":"1650","1639":"1639","1617":"1617","1627":"1627","1659":"1659","1615":"1615","1647":"1647","lifeSummary":"Mary-nic-Alexander Mackenzie of Applecross and Coul est née, fil